OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain spreading northeast for a
OL,6,Ftime in the morning. The afternoon
OL,7,Fwill be brighter with a few showers,
OL,8,Fsome of these heavy but tending to
OL,9,Fmove through quickly in brisk
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA few showers soon dying out
OL,13,Fthis evening. It will then be dry for
OL,14,Fa time before further showery
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain spread in from the
OL,16,Fwest later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
