OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,8,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,9,Fbecoming fewer later. Breezy,
OL,10,Fespecially around coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FPatchy
OL,13,Fcloud developing on Sunday but mainly
OL,14,Fdry. A few showers on Monday but
OL,15,Fmostly dry by Tuesday. Winds lighter
OL,16,Fthan of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
